title: Eddie Braves The Elements Walking From W.V. Down To TN  + People Online Offering Cash For Feet Photos + Lunchbox Tries Cold Showers!
itunes:title: Eddie Braves The Elements Walking From W.V. Down To TN  + People Online Offering Cash For Feet Photos + Lunchbox Tries Cold Showers!
description:
Eddie starts the next day of his journey from West Virginia Down to Tennessee after completing a whopping 25 miles! He is doing another 22 miles today. Morgan reveals that she gets DMs from guys asking her to take pictures of her feet. Lunchbox recorded himself taking a COLD shower after Brett Eldredge came in last week and said he does that each morning to start his day.
